  "detailed_description": "<strong>Welcome to the captivating world of \"Spot the Object\"!</strong><br><br>The ultimate hidden object game with cinematic graphics and relaxing gameplay. Embark on a delightful journey through stunning environments, where your keen eye and attention to detail will be put to the test!<br><br>Key Features:<br>🔍 <strong>Cinematic Graphics:</strong> Immerse yourself in a visually stunning environments, carefully crafted to make every scene come to life. Lose yourself in the picturesque landscapes and charming locations as you uncover hidden objects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/e36168723e4e55c9606106a06b694e3c.poster.avif?t=1691134572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/e36168723e4e55c9606106a06b694e3c.webm?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/e36168723e4e55c9606106a06b694e3c.mp4?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🎮 <strong>Casual and Relaxing:</strong> No timers, no pressure! \"Spot the Object\" provides a soothing gameplay experience for players of all ages. Take your time to explore each scene and find the objects at your own pace.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/b553f983cc02d15f01c9bb46bcdf9f58.poster.avif?t=1691134572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/b553f983cc02d15f01c9bb46bcdf9f58.webm?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/b553f983cc02d15f01c9bb46bcdf9f58.mp4?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🔎 <strong>Challenging Puzzles:</strong> Enjoy a variety of unique and brain-teasing puzzles. Sharpen your observation skills as you progress through the game.<br><br>🖼️ <strong>Stunning Environments:</strong> From mysterious forests to enchanting gardens, \"Spot the Object\" takes you on a captivating adventure through diverse and beautifully rendered settings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/affd26121337750f8da802146b40051b.poster.avif?t=1691134572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/affd26121337750f8da802146b40051b.webm?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/affd26121337750f8da802146b40051b.mp4?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🔧 <strong>Minimalistic UI:</strong> Embrace the beauty of simplicity with a clutter-free and refined user interface. Lose yourself in the game's enchanting landscapes without any distractions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/3ce7c6e200f09ef5ee4b32cfcf0ba494.poster.avif?t=1691134572\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/3ce7c6e200f09ef5ee4b32cfcf0ba494.webm?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524860/extras/3ce7c6e200f09ef5ee4b32cfcf0ba494.mp4?t=1691134572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🎶 <strong>Soothing Soundtrack:</strong> Immerse yourself in the calming melodies that accompany your hidden object quests, enhancing the overall relaxing experience.<br><br><strong>Can you uncover all the hidden objects? Embark on an enchanting journey of discovery in \"Spot the Object\" today!</strong>",
